  <logID>k__BackingField: ENTRY #0010
  logName: ARCHIVE_10_AIRSHIP CONSTRUCTION REPORT
  locationFound: 
  logDescription: "Cleanser \r\nLOG ENTRY\r\nDate and time: 06/14 14:22:07\r\nExpanding
    my search for materials to the shore has proven most useful. I have come across
    several miscellaneous sections of old airships. I am welding them together to
    create a full ship of my own. It is not only to serve as transportation, but
    as a sanctuary where no human will ever step foot again. I will bring with me
    a number of my soldiers to provide protection and also in hopes that their proximity
    to me may grant them the same enlightenment that has been weighing on my shoulders."
